iness cards, materials and your personality. Enjoy promoting your  business in a relaxed and informal atmosphere.&nbsp; <strong>Free of charge</strong> – hosted by Chamber member businesses.\r\n\r\n                  <br><br>\r\n\r\n              <!--    <strong>Hot Topic Workshops</strong> – Held monthly. Topics covered are intended to  help our member businesses grow and be successful.  Subjects have included ADA For Your Business, Disaster Preparedness and Employment Law. </p> -->\r\n<strong>Breakfast Roundtables</strong><br>\r\nBreakfast Roundtable are on hot topics on emerging employment, labor and HR issues that effect all businesses<br><br>\r\n                  </p><p><strong>Advertising Opportunities</strong><br>\r\n\r\n                  •Redwood City Street Map, a free classified listing for members <!--Redwood City Community Guide &amp; Membership  Directory, a free classified listing for members.--> <br>\r\n\r\n                  •Display of your promotional business brochures  and flyers at the Chamber Office\'s Profile Display.<br>\r\n\r\n                  •Complimentary Ribbon cuttings or Groundbreakings.<br>\r\n\r\n                  •Free listing and 25 word description of your  company on our Chamber newly designed website with link to your website <br>\r\n\r\n                  •Single E-mail advertising drops to Chamber  members <br>\r\n\r\n                  •Event  Sponsorship opportunities</p>\r\n\r\n                  <p><strong><em>Networking Opportunities </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n                  <ul type=\"disc\">\r\n\r\n                    <li>\"<a href=\"good-morning-redwood-city.php\">Good Morning Redwood       City</a>\" Breakfast held every other month, 7:45am-9:15am, Pacific Athletic       Club. Short featured presentations on what is happening in your community.</li>\r\n\r\n                    <li>•The Annual <a href=\"kainos-benefit-golf-tournament.php\">Kainos Home       &amp; Training Center For Developmentally Disabled Adults Benefit Golf       Tournament</a>, Monday May 13, 2013</li>\r\n\r\n                    <li>•<a href=\"chamber-invitational-golf-tournament.php\">Chamber Invitational       Golf Tournament</a> held at Peninsula Golf &amp;       Country Club, Monday, September 16, 2013</li>\r\n\r\n                    <li>•Annual<a href=\"redwood-city-progress-seminar.php\"> Progress Seminar</a> held April 12-14, 2013 at the Hyatt Regency, Monterey.</li>\r\n\r\n                  </ul>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"right\">\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.redwoodcitychamber.com/ecom/index.php?p=product&amp;id=3&amp;parent=2\" target=\"_blank\">Join the Chamber Today&gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"Leadership is for Everyone\";s:4:\"text\";s:1707:\"<p align=\"center\">If you could discuss  matters of importance with influential civic and community leaders in a  comfortable, open setting …<br>\r\n\r\n                   	     Would you do it?<br>\r\n\r\n           	      <br>\r\n\r\n                        	    If you could learn leadership skills, gain valuable  information and resources to aid you in your work …<br>\r\n\r\n                        	    Would you do it?<br>\r\n\r\n                   	     <br>\r\n\r\n                        	    If you could create a positive presence and  identify yourself and your organization as a partner with your community …<br>\r\n\r\n                        	    Would you do it?<br>\r\n\r\n                   	     <br>\r\n\r\n                        	    If you are willing to accept the Leadership  Challenge…<br>\r\n\r\n                        	    If you are ready to be  more effective in your Career…<br>\r\n\r\n                        	    If you are ready to make a  difference in your Community…</p>\r\n\r\n                            <p align=\"right\"><strong><a href=\"apply-redwood-city-leadership-program.php\">Then Apply Now</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n                            <h3>Leadership Program Goals</h3>\r\